{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "镇上居民1",
            "context": "你听说了吗？\\n学院的研究员离奇死亡……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "镇上居民2",
            "context": "真可怕……\\n他们到底在研究些什么东西……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "教授",
            "context": "那两人死去还没几天，\\n就已经传闻满天飞……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "是、是的……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "教授",
            "context": "听好了，此事绝对不能说出去。\\n要是被人知道我们在研究可疑的魔道书，\\n还不知道要被外面传成什么样。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "教授",
            "context": "研究也没法继续了……终止吧。\\n把那魔道书作为禁书封印起来。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "封、印……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "我回来了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "父亲",
            "context": "阿加莎，我可听说了，\\n你们学院好像有人死了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "父、父亲……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "母亲",
            "context": "魔法学的学院果然不是什么正经地方。\\n又破旧又阴森，\\n现在还闹出了人命。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "母亲……那个，其实这次\\n是发生了出乎意料的事故……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "母亲",
            "context": "老公！我本来就反对，\\n都是你说要给校长面子，\\n才同意她去学院的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "父亲",
            "context": "我也没想到……\\n她这种年纪，\\n会一头扎进那种地方出不来。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "父亲",
            "context": "之前碍于校长的面子不好让她辞职……\\n不过现在出了这种事，\\n也算有充分的理由了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "父亲",
            "context": "阿加莎，你辞职吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "辞职……\\n父亲，您在说什么……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "父亲",
            "context": "我已经写信告诉学院你要辞职了。\\n你别再做研究了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "诶？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "母亲",
            "context": "阿加莎，明天开始你要出席茶会，\\n还有派对也是。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "母亲",
            "context": "礼服也得多买一些。\\n要腾出地方放礼服……\\n你那些发霉的书就都扔掉吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "母亲",
            "context": "毕竟，你不用再做研究了嘛！\\n今后就开开心心过日子吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "（没关系，不要紧。\\n这都没什么大不了的……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "（论文也好，研究也罢，\\n还有魔道书，以及……我自己。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "（毕竟这是没有办法的事，\\n是已成定局的事。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "（毕竟、毕竟、毕竟、毕竟。\\n没办法、没办法、没办法。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "（可是……可是、可是、可是、可是。\\n更多、更多、更多、更多。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "（想要更多，可是，没办法，毕竟，\\n更多，对，更多……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "寂寞、寂寞的，孤独迷宫……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "那么……出口在何处？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "你、你是，谁？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "您猜？这样跟您说吧，\\n我只是个微不足道的祭司。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "先不说这个……我们来玩游戏吧。\\n猜谜游戏，您很喜欢吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "揭晓谜底、寻得真相，\\n一直以来您就是这样\\n找到自己的容身之处……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "你、你又知道我的什么？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "一切哦。我知晓您的过去、现在，\\n以及将来，知晓您的一切……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "知道……一切？\\n不可能，会有那种人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "哎呀……但是存在哦？就在此处。\\n您也能变成那样。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "我……也？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "呵呵……那么，来想想看？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "您的前方有一扇门。\\n上了银锁的、不可思议的门……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "那么……里面会有些什么呢？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "就、就这样？没有提示吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "没有哦？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "不过……您的选择，\\n只有两个。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "转身离去，\\n或是打开门进去。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "无论您如何想象，只要不打开门，\\n就永远无法得知真相。\\n永远……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "那、那种事！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "我怎么可能……不开门就转身离去。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "我一直解谜至今，\\n获得知识是我唯一的乐趣。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "无论发生什么，无论别人说什么，\\n哪怕孤身一人，都不要紧。\\n因为我能梦想着知识的世界！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "但是……一切都被夺走了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "没错……努力写出的论文，\\n还有教给我未知世界的魔道书。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "而如今，连依靠至今的知识\\n这一容身之处也被夺走了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "您要怎么做呢？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "猜谜的答案，\\n可以随您所想哦。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "您告诉自己那些都是没办法的事\\n而一路放弃。但实际上呢？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "这、这……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "真正的您，\\n一直以来都想怎么做呢？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "我……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "真正的、我……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "我要打开，那扇门。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0066",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "父&母",
            "context": "！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0067",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "更多、更多、更多、更多、\\n更多、更多、更多、更多、\\n更多、更多、更多、更多……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0068",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "我想，知道更多！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0069",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "父亲",
            "context": "喂、喂，阿加莎……这是怎么回事？\\n你要做什么！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0070",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "母亲",
            "context": "阿、阿加莎，你快住手……\\n妈妈我很害怕……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0071",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "来吧……伟大的知识啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0072",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "我已不再迷惘，\\n将一切归于虚无吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110341_01_03_0073",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}